page.title: 05BOURNEMOUTH RESIDENT
page.content:
I like Bournemouth for the sea and the surrounding countryside. All my friends are here. I have travelled to many parts of the world but I would not want to live anywhere else. Bournemouth has a quality about it.
Yes, there have been changes some good and some bad. The BIC takes up too much room, I think they should have built a proper swimming pool, I have only visited it once. There are good shops here but most of all my friends are here and I would not like to live anywhere else.
Tina Bondsfield, Sara Thorley, Kelly Ward. 3C
